# Resume & Portfolio Builder Tool

**2024 Project**

A web application that allows users to build professional resumes and portfolios using customizable templates and export options.

---

## Features
- User-friendly form input for personal details, education, work experience, skills, and projects
- Multiple resume and portfolio templates
- Export resumes as PDF and DOCX
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile

---

## Technologies Used
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Vanilla or React)
- PDF generation libraries (e.g., jsPDF)
- Optional backend with Node.js/Express (for saving profiles)

---

## Installation

Clone the repo and open `index.html` in a browser (for frontend-only version):

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/resume-portfolio-builder.git
cd resume-portfolio-builder
open index.html
